<section class="Services" id="Services">

  <script>
    var coll = document.getElementsByClassName("collapsible");
    var i;
      
    for (i = 0; i < coll.length; i++) {
      coll[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
        this.classList.toggle("active");
        var content = this.nextElementSibling;
        if (content.style.display === "block") {
          content.style.display = "none";
          } 
        else {
          content.style.display = "block";
          }
      });
    }
  </script>


  <h1><span>Ser</span>vices</h1>

  <button type="button" class="collapsible">Design</button>

      <div class="content">
          <p>Transforming visual ideas into a stunning reality, right from conceptualization to final execution. Designs that are not just visually captivating but also aligned with brand identity.</p>
      </div>

      <button type="button" class="collapsible">Content</button>
      <div class="content">
          <p>Tailored content solutions that meet your brand's unique needs, effectively deliver your brand message, connect with the target audience, and drive meaningful engagement. </p>
      </div>

      <button type="button" class="collapsible" id="SMM">social media marketing</button>
      <div class="content">
          <p>Making sure your brand stands out in the digital landscape by staying on top of social media trends and best practices, developing engaging content, and implementing a metrics-led strategy.</p>
      </div>
   
  </div>
  
</section>

<style>
  
  .Services > h1 {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .collapsible {
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    color: #B6E851;
    cursor: pointer;

    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border: none;
    border-top: .1rem solid #B6E851;
    
    text-align: left;
    outline: none;

    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: bold;
    }

    
    /* Add a background color to the button if it is clicked on (add the .active class with JS), and when you move the mouse over it (hover) */
    .active, .collapsible:hover {
        background-color: #6D549E;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        border-top: .1rem solid #6D549E;
    }

    /* Style the collapsible content. Note: hidden by default */
    .content {
        display: none;
        overflow: hidden;
        
        color: #6D549E;

        font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        
    }

</style>